{"tid":2372774,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇做廚房嘅巴打入嚟傾幾句？","createTime":"2021-01-20T03:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T03:36:49.000Z","uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dbacacaf63fb2613745533bf62bc31acb5289e73","tid":2372774,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T03:27:23.000Z","msg":"我係KFC廚房(唔講邊間分店)。<br />\n<br />\n成日俾水吧同執餐嗰啲妹妹仔催，我心諗催我無用嗰啵，催部炸爐仲好啦。<br />\n<br />\n啲雞至少要十五分鐘先熟，唔熟拎出去俾客食，食到出事係咪你哋負責啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed2350302b4049a625042e938644492ae8d2f4f","tid":2372774,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c7411860eb092d05f83dfcd0cbf83bc7eaaeea","tid":2372774,"uid":318634,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T03:34:23.000Z","msg":"冇記錯KFC啲炸雞炸完係會放喺個爐熱住先<br />\n<br />\n係唔會炸完即刻拎上去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你一係假膠一係廢"},{"pid":"4b5eefd6bd8aac044a98d4833ab26701bb9c6bd9","tid":2372774,"uid":294802,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T03:36:49.000Z","msg":"你只係KFC仔 唔係做廚房<br />\n你負責叮下雞架炸 唔好講到自己識煮野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你標題應該打。有冇同我一樣做緊m記/KFC 既廢柴入黎圍下爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}